	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=82400"><span id=" ">zumaVT</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">14 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>xaanru is exactly right on all accounts. Additionally, the way I read it, the other guy was only considering damage ratio and not damage bonus for primary hand in his comparisons. The only reason faster weapons will eventually out damage the wurmy is due to the increasing damage bonus as the player levels. It is the superior ratio that make the wurmy such a great weapon but at some point in the low to mid 50s, faster weapons are able to do more dps.</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
